/**
 * Email Inbox Component
 *
 * Outlook-like email interface for Alden persona with:
 * - Account selector
 * - Message list with preview
 * - Compose and sync functionality
 * - Keyboard shortcuts (r, a, f, Delete, n, j/k)
 * - Preview pane toggle (split view vs list view)
 * - Quick actions bar (archive, read/unread, flag, move)
 * - Search with highlighting
 *
